{
  "texts": [
    "Cells were grown in DMEM with 10% FBS, screened for Mycoplasma contamination by PCR and verified by short tandem repeat (STR) testing (IDEXX BioAnalytics).",
    "CRISPR-Cas9 nuclease was stably integrated by a lentivirus.",
    "LentiCas9-Blast (Addgene plasmid no.",
    "52962) and lentiCRISPR v2 (Addgene plasmid no.",
    "52961) were gifts from F. Zhang 79."
  ]
}